Description.Display: This package contains the Dell system BIOS update. BIOS is a firmware package that is embedded on a small memory chip on the system board. It controls the keyboard, monitor, disk drives, and other devices. This update addresses the Intel Technical Advisory INTEL-TA-00404.

Name.Display: Intel Rapid Storage Technology Driver and Management Console

Description.Display: This package contains the driver for the Intel Rapid Storage Technology and Management Console. Intel Rapid Storage Technology is an application that enhances the performance and reliability of Windows-based systems with storage devices.

This package contains the Intel HD Graphics driver for the Intel 6th and 7th Generation processors. A graphics or video driver is the software that enables communication between the graphics card and the operating system, games, and applications. The update addresses the Intel Security Advisories INTEL-SA-00314 and INTEL-SA-0315. A security advisory is a statement when a security vulnerability impacts a product, and a remedy is available for the vulnerability.

Device.Display: Intel HD, Iris, Iris Pro Graphics
Intel HD, Iris, Iris Pro Graphics

Name.Display: Intel I2xx/825xx Gigabit Ethernet Network Controller Driver

Description.Display: This package provides Intel I2xx/825xx 10/100/1000 Ethernet Network Driver for Precision, OptiPlex, Latitude and XPS series running the following Windows Operating Systems: Windows 7, Windows 8, Windows 8.1, Windows 10, Windows Server 2012, Windows Server 2012 R2 and Windows Server 2016.

This package contains the driver for the Realtek High Definition Audio driver. Audio driver is the software that helps your operating system to communicate with audio devices such as sound cards and speakers.

This package contains the Dell Command | Monitor application. The Dell Command | Monitor software application enables remote management of client systems. It uses application programs to access the system information, monitor the status, or change the state of the system such as remotely shutting down the system.
This package contains the Intel Serial IO driver. Intel serial IO driver enables the communication and the transfer of data between connected devices and the system.

This package contains the driver for the Intel Management Engine Components Installer. The update installs Intel Management Engine Interface, Intel Capability Licensing Service Client, Serial Over LAN Driver, Intel Wireless Management, Local Manageability Service, Local Manageability Service, Intel Converged Security and Manageability Engine (CSME) Windows Management Instrumentation (WMI) provider, and Intel Dynamic Application Loader Host Interface. This update also addresses the Intel Technical Advisory INTEL-TA-00391.

This package contains the Intel I2xx and 825xx Ethernet Network driver that supports a bandwidth of 10 Mbps, 100 Mbps, and 1000 Mbps. The Ethernet network driver helps the system to connect to a wired Internet connection.
